                        <interp inst="t18430102-name-359" type="given" value="ELIZA"></interp>ELIZA CALE</persName>
                  </hi>. I was standing at my door in West-street—I saw the pri<lb></lb>soner coming down with this carpet—the policeman crossed to him—he threw it off his shoulder, and immediately alter he ran off—I got a young man to help me with the carpet into my shop, and as soon as the officer returned with the prisoner I gave the carpet into his care.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> A man met me, and told me to carry it, and he would give me 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.</p>
